Usage: setPathGroupOptions [-help] <pathgroupName> [-early]
                           [-effortLevel {low high}] [-late]
                           [-skewingSlackConstraint <float>]
                           [-slackAdjustment <float>]
                           [-slackAdjustmentPriority <integer>]
                           [-targetSlack <float>] [-view <string>]
                           [-weight <integer>]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
<pathgroupName>                        # pathgroup name (string, required)
-early                                 # early mode only  (bool, optional)
-effortLevel {low high}                # effort level option  (enum, optional)
-late                                  # late mode only  (bool, optional)
-skewingSlackConstraint <float>        # slack constraint when skewing
                                       # (float, optional)
-slackAdjustment <float>               # slack adjustment  (float, optional)
-slackAdjustmentPriority <integer>     # slack adjustment priority 
                                       # (uint, optional)
-targetSlack <float>                   # target slack option  (float, optional)
-view <string>                         # views (string, optional)
-weight <integer>                      # optimization priority 
                                       # (uint, optional)